{Speech 21}{}{So that's how it is. Hmm, well then we have a conflict of interest. This case will have to be brought before a commission. Submit an application in the proper form, the commission will convene in a couple of weeks.}
{Speech 21 Answer 24}{}{A commission? Is that really necessary? It's a trifling matter. I'll vouch for him, and naturally I'll compensate for any damage he caused the city. And all the costs of his upkeep.}
{Speech 21 Answer 23}{}{What a drag everywhere. Commissions… I can't stand them. }
{Speech 22}{}{For those who love, yes… I can understand. [Moves closer to you] And it's even harder for one who lives without love… [Moves closer again]}
