{Speech 22 Answer 23}{}{Hey! What are you doing! Back off from me!}
{Speech 23}{}{Leave the premises. I can't help you with anything.}
{Speech 24}{}{So that's it, compensate the costs… I'll draw up the calculation now… So, the fee for your servant comes to 1284 coins. Kindly pay up.}
